<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng 迦南784</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 hěn duō nián qián de wǒ, zhèng zài jué wàng zhōng, shì yé sū qīn zì lái diǎn liàng wǒ xīn zhōng de dēng.
 hěn duō nián qián de wǒ, è guàn mǎn yíng, yé sū jìng rán wèi wǒ de zuì zài shí jià shàng bèi dīng.
 zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng, zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng. shèng guò diē niáng, shèng guò péng yǒu, zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng.
 zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng. dān dāng wǒ jí bìng, shí zì jià shàng wèi wǒ ér sǐ, ràng wǒ dé xīn shēng mìng.
 zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng, yǒng yuǎn jì xīn zhōng. bào dá zhǔ ēn fēng yǔ jiān chéng, zhǔ de ēn qíng zhòng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>784</hymn_number>
</song>